# Splunk SIEM Lab Setup

Environment:
VMware Workstation

Machines:
Ubuntu Server running Splunk Enterprise
Windows 11 endpoint

Setup Steps:

1 Install Ubuntu VM
2 Install Splunk Enterprise
3 Install Windows VM
4 Install Splunk Universal Forwarder
5 Send Windows logs to Splunk
6 Create SPL query for Event ID 4625
7 Configure real-time brute force alert
